msgctxt "84_Rumor-loving High School Girl"
msgid "You know this place called Sky Finance?"
msgstr "You know this place called Sky Finance?"

msgctxt "96_Chatty High School Girl"
msgid "Yeah. What about it?"
msgstr "Yeah. What about it?"

msgctxt "108_Rumor Loving High School Girl"
msgid "Well, it's a place that lends you money. But I\\r\n"\n"heard the owner's a hardcore criminal!"
msgstr "Well, it's a place that lends you money. But I\\r\n"\n"heard the owner's a hardcore criminal!"

msgctxt "120_Chatty High School Girl"
msgid "Seriously? What'd he do?"
msgstr "Seriously? What'd he do?"

msgctxt "132_Rumor-loving High School Girl"
msgid "They say he's a badass yakuza who, like, goes\\r\n"\n"around beating people up at random."
msgstr "They say he's a badass yakuza who, like, goes\\r\n"\n"around beating people up at random."

msgctxt "144_Chatty High School Girl"
msgid "No way! Really!? Sounds like a scary guy!"
msgstr "No way! Really!? Sounds like a scary guy!"

msgctxt "156_Rumor-loving High School Girl"
msgid "Not only that, he's killed at least 10 or 20 people!\\r\n"\n"And I heard he's been arrested tons of times, too!"
msgstr "Not only that, he's killed at least 10 or 20 people!\\r\n"\n"And I heard he's been arrested tons of times, too!"

msgctxt "168_Chatty High School Girl"
msgid "No way! How come he's not, like, in prison!?"
msgstr "No way! How come he's not, like, in prison!?"

msgctxt "180_Rumor-loving High School Girl"
msgid "Duh! 'Cause he's a moneylender! Every time he\\r\n"\n"gets arrested, he just gives the cops a boatload\\r\n"\n"of money and they let him go."
msgstr "Duh! 'Cause he's a moneylender! Every time he\\r\n"\n"gets arrested, he just gives the cops a boatload\\r\n"\n"of money and they let him go."

msgctxt "192_Chatty High School Girl"
msgid "That's totally messed up!"
msgstr "That's totally messed up!"

